        "padding": "0px",
        "maxWidth": "100%",
        "text": "<div align=\"center\">\n<div class=\"stories-heading\">Stories</div>\n<div class=\"link-container\"> \n     <a href=\"news-cn\" id=\"link1\" class=\"cmn-t-underline\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset:5px;\"  onclick=\"selectLink('link1')\">新闻</a>\n        <a href=\"city-guide-cn\" id=\"link2\" class=\"cmn-t-underline\" onclick=\"selectLink('link2')\">城市指南</a>\n        <a href=\"events-cn\" id=\"link3\" class=\"cmn-t-underline\" onclick=\"selectLink('link3')\">活动</a>\n        <a href=\"interviews-cn\" id=\"link4\" class=\"cmn-t-underline\" onclick=\"selectLink('link4')\">采访</a>\n    </div>\n</div>    \n    \n<style>\n    div {\n        white-space: normal;\n    }\n    .link-container {\n        flex-wrap: nowrap;\n        justify-content: center;\n        max-width: 100%;\n        overflow-x: auto;\n        letter-spacing: 0.8px;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        font-size: 0.875rem !important;\n        font-family: \"MessinaSans\";\n        color: #191919;\n        padding-bottom: 50px;\n    }\n    .link-container a {\n        flex: 0 0 auto;\n        margin: 5px 15px 5px 15px;\n        padding: 0 0;\n        text-decoration: none;\n        color: #191919;\n        border-radius: 5px;\n        min-width: fit-content;\n    }\n\n    .stories-heading {\n        font-weight: 200;\n        font-family: \"Miller\";\n        text-align: center !important;\n        font-size: 50px;\n        line-height: 50px;\n        color: #191919;\n        margin: 0 0 38px 0;\n    }\n\n    .cmn-t-underline {\n        position: relative;\n        color: #191919;\n    }\n    .cmn-t-underline:after {\n        display: block;\n        position: absolute;\n        right: 0;\n        bottom: -3px;\n        width: 0;\n        height: 10px;\n        background-color: #191919;\n        content: \"\";\n        -webkit-transition: all 0.3s;\n        -moz-transition: all 0.3s;\n        -o-transition: all 0.3s;\n        transition: all 0.3s;\n        height: 1px;\n    }\n    .cmn-t-underline:hover {\n        color: #191919;\n    }\n    .cmn-t-underline:hover:after {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 1px;\n    }\n\n    /* Responsive layout */\n    @media screen and (max-width: 1200px) {\n        .link-container {\n            max-width: 100%;\npadding-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n        .link-container a {\n            margin: 5px;\n            padding: 0 10px;\n        }\n   .stories-heading {\n           font-size: 28px;\n    line-height: 28px;\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    margin-bottom: 35px;\n        }\n    }\n\n    @media screen and (max-width: 800px) {\n       \t.link-container {\n            display: flex;\n\t\t\tmax-width: 100%;\n            flex-wrap: nowrap;\n            overflow-x: scroll;\n        }\n        .link-container a {\n            margin: 5px;\n            padding: 0 8px;\n            flex: 0 0 auto;\n        }\n         .stories-heading {\n           font-size: 28px;\n    line-height: 28px;\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    }\n\n    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {\n        .link-container {\n            display: flex;\n\t\t\tmax-width: 100%;\n            flex-wrap: nowrap;\n            overflow-x: scroll;\nmargin-bottom: 6px;\n        }\n        .link-container a {\n         margin: 5px auto 5px auto;\n    flex: 0 0 auto;\n        }\n        .stories-heading {\n           font-size: 28px;\n    line-height: 28px;\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    }\n</style>",
